drtblog
-----
My blog created using Hugo[1] based on Stephen Balaban's template[2].


Usage
----
Make sure you have hugo installed on your system and clone the repository:

    git clone https://github.com/drtunicorn/drtblog

Running on your local machine:

    hugo server

Build static pages:

    hugo

Command above will generate the public directory contain all the static pages then upload it to 
your preferred hosting services.


Credits
-----
Hugo - Static site generator
Stephen Balaban - Blog template

References
-------
[1] https://gohugo.io
[2] https://github.com/stephenbalaban/stephenbalaban.com
